methods.name: public Builder setSampleRate(@SampleRate int sampleRate)
methods.comment:
* Set the audio sample rate information as defined in the Generic Audio section of * Bluetooth Assigned 6.12.4.1 Supported_Sampling_Frequencies. * *

Internally this will be converted to Sampling_Frequency values as defined in 6.12.5.1 * * @param sampleRate configured sample rate in meta data * @return this builder * @throws IllegalArgumentException if sample rate is invalid value * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setFrameDuration(@FrameDuration int frameDuration)
methods.comment:
* Set the audio frame duration information as defined in the Generic Audio section of * Bluetooth Assigned numbers 6.12.5.2 Frame_Duration. * *

Internally this will be converted to Frame_Durations values as defined in 6.12.4.2 * * @param frameDuration configured frame duration in meta data * @return this builder * @throws IllegalArgumentException if frameDuration is invalid value * @hide
